TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Optional lookup to get the alias lead time from MFG_PATH x MFG_PATH_CHP join
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CASE NVL(MPC.MFG_PATH_ID, '0') WHEN '0' THEN (CASE MP.MAKE_OR_BUY_CD WHEN 'B' THEN TO_NUMBER($$PARM_BUY_LEAD_TIME) ELSE TO_NUMBER($$PARM_MAKE_LEAD_TIME) END) ELSE (MPC.LEAD_TIME * 7) END AS ALIAS_LEAD_TIME, CASE NVL(MPC.MFG_PATH_ID, '0') WHEN '0' THEN (CASE MP.MAKE_OR_BUY_CD WHEN 'B' THEN TO_CHAR($$PARM_BUY_LEAD_TIME) ELSE TO_CHAR($$PARM_MAKE_LEAD_TIME) END) ELSE ('MFG_PATH_CHP for path ' || MPC.MFG_PATH_ID || ' and revision_no ' || MPC.REVISION_NO) END AS ALIAS_LEAD_TIME_SOURCE, MP.STYLE_CD AS STYLE_CD, MP.COLOR_CD AS COLOR_CD, MP.ATTRIBUTE_CD AS ATTRIBUTE_CD, MP.SIZE_CD AS SIZE_CD FROM MFG_PATH MP LEFT JOIN MFG_PATH_CHP MPC ON (MP.STYLE_CD = MPC.STYLE_CD AND MP.COLOR_CD = MPC.COLOR_CD AND MP.ATTRIBUTE_CD = MPC.ATTRIBUTE_CD AND MP.SIZE_CD = MPC.SIZE_CD AND MP.MFG_PATH_ID = MPC.MFG_PATH_ID AND MP.REVISION_NO = MPC.REVISION_NO) WHERE MP.CORP_STD_PATH_IND = 'Y'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_ALIAS_STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CD = I_ALIAS_COLOR_CD AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ALIAS_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_ALIAS_SIZE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: To derive Lead time
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_GET_LEAD_TIME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_LKP_DPR_DIR_SHP_LEADTIME) AND I_LKP_DPR_DIR_SHP_LEADTIME>0,I_LKP_DPR_DIR_SHP_LEADTIME, IIF(NOT ISNULL(V_LKP1_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME) AND V_LKP1_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME>0,V_LKP1_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME, IIF(NOT ISNULL(V_LKP2_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME) AND V_LKP2_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME>0,V_LKP2_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME, IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_LKP1_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME) AND I_LKP1_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME>0,I_LKP1_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME, IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME) AND I_LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME>0,I_LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME, TO_DECIMAL($$PARM_MAKE_LEAD_TIME))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_ALIAS_LEAD_TIME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_LKP_DPR_DIR_SHP_LEADTIME) AND I_LKP_DPR_DIR_SHP_LEADTIME>0, ('DPR_DIRECT_SHIP for location ' || I_LKP_DPR_DIR_SHP_DEMAND_LOC), IIF(NOT ISNULL(V_LKP1_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME) AND V_LKP1_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME>0, ('DPR_CUMULATIVE_LEADTIME for corp_business_unit '|| I_CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT), IIF(NOT ISNULL(V_LKP2_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME) AND V_LKP2_DPR_LDTM_LEADTIME>0,('DPR_CUMULATIVE_LEADTIME for corp_business_unit '|| I_CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT), IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_LKP1_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME) AND I_LKP1_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME>0,I_LKP1_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME_SOURCE, IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME) AND I_LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME>0,I_LKP2_MFG_PATH_LEADTIME_SOURCE, $$PARM_MAKE_LEAD_TIME)))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_ALIAS_LEAD_TIME_SOURCE
